Invocation Name: i. c. d. helper
des:
In today's world, many diagnoses have ICD-10 codes associated with them - and furthermore, there is a hierarchical structure with details for every ICD-10 code. Even the most experienced coders have to search codes up frequently. ICD-10 Helper is a quick and easy way to get descriptions and full names of diagnostic codes using the most recent ICD-10 lists.
